Off the field, Milner is known for his professionalism and dedication to his craft. He has set up his own charity, the James Milner Foundation, which supports local communities and young people. In 2018, he was appointed an MBE for his services to football and charity work.

Despite being in the twilight of his career, Milner continues to be an influential player for Orlando City SC, and is widely respected for his leadership, work ethic, and commitment to the game.
